    <h1>The Beauty of Hawaii</h1>

    <h2>Why People Love the Islands</h2>

    <p>
        Hawaii is known for its <strong>beautiful beaches</strong>, 
        <em>warm weather</em>, and rich culture. Many visitors enjoy 
        learning about local traditions and exploring nature. 
        One popular activity is hiking near volcanic landscapes. 
        <br><br>
        The islands also offer amazing food, music, and ocean views. 
        People from around the world visit Hawaii to relax and experience 
        the spirit of <mark>aloha</mark>.
    </p>

    <hr>

    <blockquote>
        "The loveliest fleet of islands that lies anchored in any ocean."
        — Mark Twain
    </blockquote>

